               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Mas̲navī-'i maʿnavī by Rūmī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2002009961" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1295x-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic </textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Daftar I of the Mas̲navī-'i maʿnavī by "Rūmī" Mawlānā Jalāl al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn Muḥammad Bahāʾ al-Dīn Valad Balkhī (d. 670/1271). </p>
                        <p>Partially dated colophon (f. 77r): completed by Mīrzā Muḥammad, Tuesday, in Z̲ī al-Ḥijjah (year not stated). 
</p>
                        <p>Rough nastaʿlīq in two main columns, following  on into margins. 
</p>
                        <p>Folios cropped; substantial gouges at beginning; wormholes, later repairs. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100166176928.0x000001 viaf_98930150">Rūmī</persName>
